“Crosscurrents in Gao Xingjian’s Apocalyptic Total Theatre and Linguistic Ingenuity: Globalization, Avant-Gardism, and Oriental Metaphysical Practice”
C PRACSIS International Conference on “Body, Space, and Technology” at Thrissur
